Internet Gateway
Private subnet should be used for resources that wont be allowed access to internet

NAT gateway - enables instances in private subnet to initiate outbound traffic to the internet.
NAT gateway will always inside a public subnet

We have range of ips.. but address reserved for Private are 10.0.0.0/24 (CIDR to IP adress)
ip address are bit format

8 bits . 8bits. 8bits. 8bits

00001010  00000000 00000000. (24 bits are fixed)  only last 8 bits are allowed to changed

